description: This resource shows the latest void-filled version of the Shuttle Radar Topography Mission (SRTM) digital elevation model for Kwale county at a spatial resolution of 30 meters. Here, the data has been modeled to illustrates areas that are below 30 meters i.e. areas prone to sea-level rise, etc.
keywords: model, elevation, digital, Africa, East Africa, Kenya
name: Digital Elevation Model (30 m)
